          "evidence_text_excerpt": "e accountholders, you will need to save $200 or more a month across all of your accounts to qualify for Smart Interest. Smart Interest will be earned on your total balances across these accounts, up to $200,000 (the \"Smart Balance Maximum\").\nIf you have multiple accounts with different accountholders (for example, an account you own individually and a joint account you own with another person), Smart Interest will be calculated separately. This means you will need to save $200 or more each month in each account. The Smart Balance Maximum of $200,000 will apply to each account when calculating Smart Interest.\nYou'll earn Smart Interest up to the Smart Balance Maximum independently from and in addition to other offers.\nNew Account special Interest Rate Offer: Get a special interest offer for 3 months when you open your first CIBC eAdvantage Savings Account. \u24d8 Learn more",
